Pipeline Operations.aiplatform.PipelineJob: Creates and runs a pipeline job.
Pipeline Operations.aiplatform.PipelineJob.submit: Submits a pipeline job for execution.
Pipeline Operations.aiplatform.PipelineJob.wait_for_completi: Waits for a pipeline job to complete.

Model Operations.aiplatform.Model.upload: Uploads a machine learning model to Vertex AI.
Model Operations.aiplatform.Model.deploy: Deploys a model to an endpoint.
Model Operations.aiplatform.Model.delete: Deletes the model from the cloud.
Model Operations.aiplatform.Model.export: Exports a model to a specified location.
Model Operations.aiplatform.Model.evaluate: Evaluates the performance of a deployed model.

Endpoint Operations.aiplatform.Endpoint.create: Creates a new endpoint to deploy models.
Endpoint Operations.aiplatform.Endpoint.deploy: Deploys a model to an existing endpoint.
Endpoint Operations.aiplatform.Endpoint.undeploy: Undeploys a model from an endpoint.
Endpoint Operations.aiplatform.Endpoint.predict: Makes predictions on the deployed model.

Dataset Operations.aiplatform.Dataset.create: Creates a dataset in Vertex AI.
Dataset Operations.aiplatform.Dataset.import_data: Imports data into the dataset from Cloud Storage or BigQuery.

Training Jobs.aiplatform.CustomJob.create: Creates a custom training job with specified resources.
Training Jobs.aiplatform.CustomJob.submit: Submits a custom job for execution.

AutoML Operations.aiplatform.AutoMLTabularTrainingJob: Trains a tabular dataset with AutoML.
AutoML Operations.aiplatform.AutoMLImageTrainingJob: Trains an image dataset with AutoML.
AutoML Operations.aiplatform.AutoMLTextTrainingJob: Trains a text dataset with AutoML.
AutoML Operations.aiplatform.AutoMLVideoTrainingJob: Trains a video dataset with AutoML.

Batch Prediction Jobs.aiplatform.BatchPredictionJob.wait_for_c: Waits for a batch prediction job to complete.

Hyperparameter Tuning Jobs.aiplatform.HyperparameterTuningJob.wait_: Waits for the tuning job to complete.

Other Utility Operations.aiplatform.init: Initializes the Vertex AI environment and settings.
Other Utility Operations.aiplatform.log_metrics: Logs evaluation metrics in an experiment.
